## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias in the articles reviewed. The perspectives are primarily from sources that oppose steroid use, which may not fully represent the arguments of those who support it. Additionally, the data is up to date only until October 2023, and newer studies or findings may not be included.

